Class AutomatedTestCaseQuestionAnswer.TestResult

java.lang.Object
application.AutomatedTestCaseQuestionAnswer.TestResult
Enclosing class:
AutomatedTestCaseQuestionAnswer
public static class AutomatedTestCaseQuestionAnswer.TestResult extends Object
Represents the result of a test case execution. Contains information about the test name, whether it passed, and a message.
